en: Are you sure you want to create a new project? All unsaved changes will be lost.
zh: 您确定要创建一个新项目吗？所有未保存的更改将丢失。

en: Please select an icon group in the list to edit
zh: 请在左侧列表中选择一个图案组进行编辑

en: Please select an icon to edit its detail
zh: 请选择一个图案以编辑详情

en: Please manage the paths to UI sprite scan folders in the text edit below. The scan folders are for automatically matching the UI sprite files, based on textures' filen names, when importing banner icon textures.\nEach line is a relative folder path to the texture location.
zh: 请在下方填写UI图标扫描目录的路径，用于在导入旗帜贴图时，通过文件名自动匹配UI图标文件。\n每行对应一个扫描目录，目录路径是基于贴图文件的相对路径。
